ENTRY       EC 2.4.1.31                 Enzyme
NAME        laminaribiose phosphorylase
CLASS       Transferases;
            Glycosyltransferases;
            Hexosyltransferases
SYSNAME     3-beta-D-glucosyl-D-glucose:phosphate alpha-D-glucosyltransferase
REACTION    3-beta-D-glucosyl-D-glucose + phosphate = D-glucose + alpha-D-glucose 1-phosphate [RN:R00953 R06058]
ALL_REAC    R00953 R06058(G)
SUBSTRATE   3-beta-D-glucosyl-D-glucose [CPD:C02048];
            phosphate [CPD:C00009]
PRODUCT     D-glucose [CPD:C00031];
            alpha-D-glucose 1-phosphate [CPD:C00103]
COMMENT     Also acts on 1,3-beta-D-oligoglucans. Differs in specificity from EC 2.4.1.30 (1,3-beta-oligoglucan phosphorylase) and EC 2.4.1.97 (1,3-beta-D-glucan phosphorylase).
